            <li>Waste percentage (typical ice cream waste ranges from 2-5%)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-4">Step 3: Enter Your Business Expenses</h3>
        <p class="mt-4">
            Input your monthly fixed costs:
