        <p class="mt-4">
            Click "Calculate Ice Cream Profit" to generate detailed projections, including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Daily, monthly, and annual sales figures</li>
            <li>Profit per unit for each menu item</li>
            <li>5-year business projection with industry survival milestones</li>
            <li>Seasonal monthly projection accounting for high and low seasons</li>
            <li>Detailed expense breakdown</li>
        </ul>

