                <ul class="list-none space-y-1">
                    <li><strong>Price per Unit:</strong> $5.00</li>
                    <li><strong>Units Sold per Day:</strong> 80</li>
                    <li><strong>Cost of Ingredients:</strong> $0.90</li>
                    <li><strong>Packaging Costs:</strong> $0.35</li>
                </ul>
