                <p class="text-sm italic">Daily Cost: 80 × ($0.90 + $0.35) = $100.00</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pl-4 border-l-4 border-gray-300 my-4">
                <p class="font-bold">Item 1: Sundae</p>
                <ul class="list-none space-y-1">
                    <li><strong>Price per Unit:</strong> $7.50</li>
                    <li><strong>Units Sold per Day:</strong> 40</li>
                    <li><strong>Cost of Ingredients:</strong> $1.50</li>
                    <li><strong>Packaging Costs:</strong> $0.50</li>
                </ul>
